value.0: Power paks or power cells provide energy for many vehicles, and small blaster weapons. Most power cells contain concentrated amounts of gases that, when heated, form plasma. In small blasters, power cells are used to create blaster bolts that are not nearly as powerful as blasters using a combination of magazines containing gases (that after being heated would change into plasma) and proper Blaster power packs. A small power cell could be used to power a prosthetic without the need for recharging.
